                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="process_content" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;1. Cycle 0: Train from scratch (50 epochs)&lt;br&gt;2. Evaluate on validation, save best model&lt;br&gt;3. Test on test period (21 days)&lt;br&gt;4. Shift all windows +21 days&lt;br&gt;5. Cycle 1+: Fine-tune (10 epochs)&lt;br&gt;6. Repeat until data exhausted&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;" parent="1" vertex="1">
